        <h4>响应式内嵌</h4>
        <p>为了使嵌入的视频支持响应式，提供一个带 <code class="language-markup">video-container</code>的div包裹着视频就行。</p>
        <div class="video-container">
          <iframe height=853 width=480 src="http://player.youku.com/embed/XNzMxNzY0NjYw" frameborder=0 allowfullscreen></iframe>
        </div>
        <pre><code class="language-markup">
